<DOCNO> APW19990621.0156 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-21 15:40:10 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> DeShields Goes on 15-Day DL </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
